About this item

  • Kids Sport Watch: Our kids fitness tracker watch does not need to connect to the phone or any app, and it's really easy to set. We integrated the step counting, stopwatch, calories, and mileage inside the watch. Record the kid's sports data.
  • Powerful Battery Life: This kids digital watch has a USB interface. You can use any USB adapter (Such as a smartphone adapter, computer, or Portable Charger) to charge the boys watch. The battery life is about 15 days.
  • Silent Vibrating Alarm: Parents can set up two alarms to remind children to study and rest on time. Whether in the classroom or the dormitory, the child can feel a vibration, but no one else will be disturbed. This is a great choice for students!
  • Reliable Quality: The best kids watch is really light and soft on the skin. The shape is also really adorable. The band has many adjustable settings and is very soft and flexible for tiny childrens wrists.
  • Waterproof Resistant: Boys digital watch has been 5 ATM water-resistant, suitable for washing hands, facial washing, and rain. This is very practical. But it is not recommended to wear it when swimming, in hot baths and in saunas.

Water-Resistant

This watch kids have been water-resistant, and suitable for washing hands, facial washing, and rain. This is very practical. But should not be used in bathing, sauna, and other multi-water or high warm environments.


USB Charging

  • USB charging, convenient and fast, no longer worry about watch power is not enough.
  • Compared to traditional watches, it has a stronger service life, so you don't have to worry about its battery running out and not being able to replace it.


Battery Life

  • It takes 1hour to fully charge, and hold work/standby 10/20days.
  • It should be noted that because the habits of each child are different, the battery life of the watch may change.

NOTE:

  • Since the watch is not a professional measuring tool, the data is for reference only and has certain errors.
  • Waterproofing tests are carried out under static conditions. The pressure of the water while wearing the watch is much higher than in the static test. Therefore, the number of meters shown on the watch does not indicate the depth the watch can reach when worn.
  • The watch can withstand a slight splash of water, but should try to avoid immersion in water.Do not press the button under water, frequent contact with water will reduce the service life of the watch.
  • Tests in sports and calories are only used as a reference and cannot be used for medical purposes. Thank you for your understanding.
